White Tree Fruit is a food acquired by picking the White tree in the Varrock palace garden, after the Garden of Tranquillity quest. The tree grows one fruit approximately every 5 minutes and can hold up to 4 fruit at a time. Picking one grants 12 Farming experience.

When eaten, it restores 5-10% run energy and heals 3 health. It is a slightly more accessible alternative to Strange fruit if players do not have access to Great Kourend.

Due to being non-tradeable unlike other fruit, it cannot be turned to banknotes neither by Tool Leprechaun nor in bank.
